{"tid":1809664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜機場遭「撫摸侵犯」影片曝光！","createTime":"2020-01-03T09:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T09:52:19.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"37f0e8872df60e5e904c1cd56b06cf79ecec1898","tid":1809664,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE人氣爆棚，卻也有許多瘋狂粉絲做出不規矩舉動，日前一名德國男粉絲因為「幻想娜璉是自己女朋友」，實際飛到首爾並四處打聽行蹤，沒想到現在連子瑜都成了受害者，一名男粉絲被拍到在機場對子瑜「伸出魔爪」，子瑜嚇得趕緊貼到團員身邊，看起來受到不小驚嚇。<br />\n<br />\n推特上近日流傳一則影片，TWICE現身機場被大批粉絲包圍，子瑜走在團隊最後面，身邊保鑣伸手從背後環住她，但此時一名金髮男走到她身後，先是輕拉她的連帽外套，再伸出手在她肩上撫摸了好幾下，還帶著開心的笑容，她發現被摸後，表情立刻變得緊張害怕，趕緊貼住前面團員，卻並未發怒，似乎在默默忍耐，模樣令人心疼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4623/d4623122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4623%2Fd4623122.jpg&h=92beb6c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜機場遭金髮男伸魔爪。（圖／翻攝自推特／misayeon）<br />\n<br />\n有粉絲將這段影片PO上網，怒斥該名男粉絲太超過，更警告：「子瑜顯得很不舒服，如果真的是粉絲，請不要對她們做這種事情！」其他粉絲看到後，紛紛暴怒留言「真想把他手扭斷」、「不要碰她」、「被陌生人這樣碰真的超噁心」、「太可惡了」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4623/d4623121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4623%2Fd4623121.jpg&h=1c31b127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜露出害怕表情。（圖／翻攝自推特／misayeon）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，被朋友揭露「幻想娜璉是自己女朋友」的TWICE德國男粉絲之前也惹出風波，實際飛到南韓首爾並四處打聽對方行蹤消息曝光後，讓全世界ONCE（官方粉絲名稱）都相當擔心。沒想到1日TWICE搭乘飛機回韓時，該名男粉絲竟然也搭乘同台飛機並試圖接近，場面一片混亂。<br />\n<br />\n對此，JYP娛樂透露已經多次向德國跟蹤狂表示「請不要試圖接近成員」並且嚴厲警告，甚至就連警方也親自出面警示對方，但該男子完全沒有反省或停止不當行為。因此，公司已經採取最高強度的法律措施並加強保全，另外也對販售藝人航班訊息的非法狀況進行瞭解：「我司以本次案件作為契機將嘗試各種可以根除犯罪的方案。」<br />\n<br />\n    Please know your boundaries as a fan. TWICE doesn&rsquo;t want to be touched like this and Tzuyu was clearly uncomfortable&hellip; If you're a fan at all don&rsquo;t do this kind of thing to them please<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想扮唔小心一野渣落去"},{"pid":"f72a3f8828b00db238f1284f8dcccd17f6e093ef","tid":1809664,"uid":256952,"like":56,"dislike":67,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"有人掂都偷笑啦 自己知自己污糟"},{"pid":"56dfa7d913f32dd26479246b9737a522088a64a8","tid":1809664,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我射撚死條仆街"},{"pid":"c3561f7feae33cb5fd69fc2aef16279e6b524b24","tid":1809664,"uid":256952,"like":7,"dislike":18,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"f72a3f8828b00db238f1284f8dcccd17f6e093ef","tid":1809664,"uid":256952,"like":56,"dislike":67,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"有人掂都偷笑啦 自己知自己污糟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"支持層主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bfcd333a368896004948b0a91feaf77fab1841","tid":1809664,"uid":231908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep